Screen Open 0,320,256,32,Lowres
Curs Off : Cls 0 : Flash Off : Hide 
Palette $0,$111,$222,$333,$444,$555,$666,$777,$888,$999,$AAA,$BBB,$CCC,$DDD,$EEE,$FFF,$EEE,$DDD,$CCC,$BBB,$AAA,$999,$888,$777,$666,$555,$444,$333,$222,$111,$0
'
Screen Open 1,320,256,32,Lowres
Curs Off : Cls 0 : Hide : Flash Off 
Get Palette 0
Screen To Back 1
'
Screen 1
'
Degree 
'
CO=0
TIM=2
'
For X=0 To 320
   Ink CO
   Draw X,0 To X,256
   If TIM=10
      Inc CO
      TIM=0
   End If 
   If CO>30
      CO=0
   End If 
   Inc TIM
Next X
'
For Y=0 To 256
   P#=Sin(POS#)*25
   Screen Copy 1,0,Y,320,Y+1 To 0,P#,Y
   POS#=POS#+10
Next Y
'
Screen Copy 0,0,0,320,256 To 1,0,0
'
For X=0 To 320
   P#=Sin(POS#)*25
   Screen Copy 1,X,0,X+1,256 To 0,X,P#
   POS#=POS#+10
Next X
'
Screen 0
